OL,3,CLyrid meteor shower: How and when to
OL,4,Cwatch 'shooting stars' peak
OL,6,FThe Lyrid meteor shower is one of the
OL,7,Foldest recorded celestial events,
OL,8,Fhaving first been recorded nearly
OL,9,F3,000 years ago, and it peaks tonight.
OL,11,FBut what are meteor showers, and where
OL,12,Fis the best place to see them? ITV
OL,13,FNews explains everything you need to
OL,14,Fknow.
OL,16,FWhat are meteor showers, and what do
OL,17,Fthey actually look like?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
