OL,3,CLyrid meteor shower: How and when to
OL,4,Cwatch 'shooting stars' peak
OL,6,FIn fact, a meteor shower looks like
OL,7,Flots of "shooting stars" in the sky
OL,8,Fover a short period of time.
OL,10,FThe different meteor shower events
OL,11,Foccur throughout the year as Earth
OL,12,Fregularly passes through the same dust
OL,13,Ftrails during its annual orbit.
OL,15,FWhy are they called Lyrids?
OL,17,FLyrids are named after the
OL,18,Fconstellation Lyra, because the
OL,19,Fmeteors appear to radiate from this
OL,20,Farea of the sky.
OL,26,@oD@IOUoD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
